metadata.name: Traveler #148
metadata.description:
Retro sci-fi style landscape sketch drawn by code.

Features:
- Terrain: Cliff, Cavern, Sky, Megalopolis, Desert, Sea, Space, Volcano
- Orientation: Landscape, Portlait
- Palette: White, Cream, Tan, Pink, Green, Yellow, Orange
- Background: Light, Dark

Live view options:
- Press "s" key: Saves the high resolution image (4200 x 3300 for landscape, 3300 x 4200 for portlait)

Depending on the device you run it on, it may take some time for the drawing to complete.
Made with p5js.

June 2022
ykxotkx

metadata.name: Unicorn #2860
metadata.description:
All of us have dreams, and everyone would like to meet a fairy, a genie, a wizard, or someone else who will make our dreams come true in a snap of a finger or with the wave of a wand. But we're the only ones who can do it. We are those magical unicorns, unique, inimitable, with our own qualities and magical abilities.
These unicorns are the visualization of our inner selves that makes our dreams come true. An embodiment of all the best with a huge positive magical power.

Twitter: @unicorn_nft_art
Web: https://unicorn-nft.web.app/
